{{zh-hanzi|[[趴]][[趴]][[走]]}}
==Chinese==
===[[w:Taiwanese Mandarin|Taiwanese Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: pā pā zŏu
===Etymology===
[[transliteration]] from [[Min Nan]]: [[拋拋走]] ([[pha-pha-cháu]]).
*pha ([[拋]]): ''to freely roam about as one pleases'' + cháu ([[走]]): ''to run''

===Idiom===
# to run all over the place; to go all over the place; to rush about or around

===Synonyms===
*Standard Mandarin: [[東奔西跑]], [[东奔西跑]]

===Notes===
*This phrase is the genesis for the name of a popular navigation software package called [[w:Papago|PaPaGO]] (Maction Software).

